title: Hour 2 - More Kevin Durant Trade Discussion, SEC Commissioner Greg Sankey
itunes:title: Hour 2 - More Kevin Durant Trade Discussion, SEC Commissioner Greg Sankey
description:
Dan dives deeper on Kevin Durant's trade request and he talks to SEC Commissioner Greg Sankey about the recent upheaval in college athletics and the future of the SEC in particular.
